of-thousands-demand-hostage-deal-on-third-day-of-rage-protests/00000191-b403-d95b-a1d5-bd3f47760000</guid></item><item><title>赫什的家人值得拜登、哈里斯和特朗普的思念和祈祷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-02/ty-article/.highlight/hershs-family-deserves-more-than-thoughts-and-prayers-from-biden-harris-and-trump/00000191-b390-dc3b-a7df-f3d050700000</link><description>如果美国立法者和官员真的想向赫什·戈德堡-波林、乔恩和雷切尔致敬，他们就必须公开呼吁达成一项能够确保赫什活着回家的协议</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 17:37:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-02/ty-article/.highlight/hershs-family-deserves-more-than-thoughts-and-prayers-from-biden-harris-and-trump/00000191-b390-dc3b-a7df-f3d050700000</guid></item><item><title>“我们让你失望了”：数千人聚集埋葬被哈马斯谋杀的以色列裔美国人质赫什·戈德堡-波林</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/thousands-gather-to-bury-hersh-goldberg-polin-israeli-american-hostage-killed-by-hamas/00000191-b333-db99-a1d1-bf7fb99e0000</link><description>赫什·戈德堡-波林和其他五名人质在加沙被哈马斯囚禁期间被处决。在他的葬礼上，以色列总统艾萨克·赫尔佐格说：“我想说，我们没能把他带回家，我感到非常遗憾”</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 17:34:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/thousands-gather-to-bury-hersh-goldberg-polin-israeli-american-hostage-killed-by-hamas/00000191-b333-db99-a1d1-bf7fb99e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第332天：拜登称内塔尼亚胡在确保人质协议方面做得不够</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-332-netanyahu-not-doing-enough-to-secure-hostage-deal-biden-says/00000191-b3bf-dd1b-a7db-b7ff81db0001</link><description>据报道，美国正在制定最终的“接受或放弃”停火提案 ■ 本-格维尔表示，他“并不羞于说”，他正在利用自己在政府中的权力“阻止一项鲁莽的协议，并完全停止任何谈判” ■ 数千人全国各地的以色列人抗议支持人质协议 ■ 英国宣布暂停向以色列运送一系列武器 ■ 战争进入 332 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 17:24:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-332-netanyahu-not-doing-enough-to-secure-hostage-deal-biden-says/00000191-b3bf-dd1b-a7db-b7ff81db0001</guid></item><item><title>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡，邪恶的救世主，领导着谎言和死亡的邪教</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/benjamin-netanyahu-the-vile-messiah-leading-a-cult-of-lies-and-death/00000191-b286-d93f-a5bb-b3967ae70000</link><description>尽管总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）主持了许多失败 — — 包括伊朗、经济、生活成本和 10 月 7 日 — — 但仍然受到超过四分之一的以色列人的崇拜。他的失败和他的支持之间的差距具有邪教的所有特征</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 17:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/benjamin-netanyahu-the-vile-messiah-leading-a-cult-of-lies-and-death/00000191-b286-d93f-a5bb-b3967ae70000</guid></item><item><title>被以色列杀害后，这位年轻的 TikToker 成为加沙迷失一代的象征</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-being-killed-by-israel-young-tiktoker-becomes-a-symbol-of-gazas-lost-generation/00000191-b359-dc3b-a7df-f35928e90000</link><description>19 岁的梅多·哈利米 (Medo Halimy) 凭借讲述加沙日常生活的乐观视频在网上走红。上周，他在一家临时咖啡馆上网时被杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 17:03:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-being-killed-by-israel-young-tiktoker-becomes-a-symbol-of-gazas-lost-generation/00000191-b359-dc3b-a7df-f35928e90000</guid></item><item><title>英国暂停向以色列出售部分武器，理由是加沙存在违反国际法的“明显风险”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/u-k-suspends-some-arms-sales-to-israel-citing-clear-risk-of-intl-law-breach-in-gaza/00000191-b38e-dc3b-a7df-f3def2160000</link><description>这是自加沙冲突开始以来西方政府采取的最严厉行动之一，可能会鼓励其他国家采取类似措施</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 16:39:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/u-k-suspends-some-arms-sales-to-israel-citing-clear-risk-of-intl-law-breach-in-gaza/00000191-b38e-dc3b-a7df-f3def2160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯社区向加沙捐赠数十吨援助物资，但以色列阻止其进入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-arab-community-donated-dozens-of-tons-of-aid-to-gaza-but-israel-blocks-its-entry/00000191-a8a6-d3dd-a991-a8be2e7d0000</link><description>以色列阿拉伯社区的一位领导人表示，“没有理由长期储存这些捐款，因为有些可能会变质”，因为以色列军队声称这些捐款不符合进入加沙的条件</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:10:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-arab-community-donated-dozens-of-tons-of-aid-to-gaza-but-israel-blocks-its-entry/00000191-a8a6-d3dd-a991-a8be2e7d0000</guid></item><item><title>“嗨，我是李比。我想告诉你我的兄弟赫什·戈德堡-波林是加沙的人质”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-09-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hi-its-leebie-i-wanted-to-tell-you-my-brother-hersh-is-a-hostage-in-gaza/00000191-b215-d27a-a1b3-ba3510410000</link><description>10 月 7 日三周后，赫什·戈德堡-波林的妹妹联系了国土报的阿米尔·蒂邦，他本人也是哈马斯袭击的幸存者。已故人质的家人直到最后一刻仍保持乐观</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:07:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-09-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hi-its-leebie-i-wanted-to-tell-you-my-brother-hersh-is-a-hostage-in-gaza/00000191-b215-d27a-a1b3-ba3510410000</guid></item><item><title>“社区对此非常渴望”：以色列南部最大的医院开设了一个新的 LGBTQ 诊所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-the-shadow-of-war-southern-israels-largest-hospital-gets-a-new-lgbtq-clinic/00000191-9d90-df07-a3b9-fddc232b0000</link><description>当 Inbar Izhak 提议在索罗卡医院为酷儿社区开设第一家妇科诊所时，她得到了那些想要安全、知情护理的人们的“疯狂顺风”。对于诊所的首席医生 Iris Shoham 来说，这项工作充满了灵性：“就像上帝在房间里一样”</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 13:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-the-shadow-of-war-southern-israels-largest-hospital-gets-a-new-lgbtq-clinic/00000191-9d90-df07-a3b9-fddc232b0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的六名人质是怎么死的？阿拉伯世界无法决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/how-did-the-six-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-die-the-arab-world-cant-decide/00000191-b227-dd49-afd3-b77774350000</link><description>社交媒体上的猜测甚嚣尘上，有人说哈马斯处决人质是针对以色列社会的心理战的一部分，而另一些人则转而否认，将人质的死亡归咎于以色列</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 12:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/how-did-the-six-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-die-the-arab-world-cant-decide/00000191-b227-dd49-afd3-b77774350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空军官员：如果没有美国的援助，以色列几个月后无法与加沙作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/without-u-s-aid-israel-would-have-struggled-to-fight-in-gaza-beyond-a-few-months/00000191-aec2-d875-a3bb-aed7e2e30000</link><description>一名高级空军军官还告诉国土报，国际合作挫败了伊朗 4 月份的袭击，并在 8 月份对真主党发动了先发制人的打击，以色列正在努力减少这种依赖</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 12:12:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/without-u-s-aid-israel-would-have-struggled-to-fight-in-gaza-beyond-a-few-months/00000191-aec2-d875-a3bb-aed7e2e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方公布照片证明本-格维尔和助手受邀发射先进武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-release-pictures-proving-ben-gvir-and-aides-invited-to-fire-advanced-weapons/00000191-b22d-d835-aff3-b3ed98c00000</link><description>2023 年 8 月，国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔 (Itamar Ben-Gvir) 参观了一个特种部队的训练基地，他、他的参谋长和驾驶员在那里被允许操作先进武器，这是一项非同寻常的行为。只有《国土报》向法庭请愿才披露了这一非同寻常事件的照片。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 12:00:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-release-pictures-proving-ben-gvir-and-aides-invited-to-fire-advanced-weapons/00000191-b22d-d835-aff3-b3ed98c00000</guid></item><item><title>除非周日的强烈抗议活动继续下去，否则以色列血淋淋的内阁不会停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-blood-soaked-cabinet-wont-stop-if-sundays-protests-were-a-one-off/00000191-b1ec-d67d-a7f5-fbee8a3f0000</link><description>就像 10 月 7 日之后的几个小时一样，越来越明显的是，内塔尼亚胡完全失去了功能，他的个人和政治生存比人质的生命重要一千倍。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 11:43:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-blood-soaked-cabinet-wont-stop-if-sundays-protests-were-a-one-off/00000191-b1ec-d67d-a7f5-fbee8a3f0000</guid></item><item><title>球迷因国歌发生冲突后，阿拉伯以色列领先足球队的比赛被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/leading-arab-israeli-soccer-teams-game-scrapped-after-fans-clash-over-national-anthem/00000191-b21c-d93f-a5bb-b31edaf20000</link><description>Bnei Sakhnin 的球员在球迷与贝尔谢巴夏普尔队的球迷发生冲突后拒绝返回球场</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 11:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/leading-arab-israeli-soccer-teams-game-scrapped-after-fans-clash-over-national-anthem/00000191-b21c-d93f-a5bb-b31edaf20000</guid></item></channel></rss>